1
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:52,479
Where's the money?

2
00:00:53,359 --> 00:00:54,600
I've been looking for you for months,

3
00:00:54,679 --> 00:00:55,719
and you haven't paid me a penny.

4
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:56,560
What do you mean?

5
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,039
Listen,

6
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,799
my wife needs to eat,

7
00:01:00,039 --> 00:01:01,399
and my kid needs to go to school.

8
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,520
If you push me too far,

9
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,159
I'll do anything.

10
00:01:04,359 --> 00:01:04,920
But I...

11
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,439
I really don't have any money.

12
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:08,120
You... you let me think of a way.

13
00:01:08,239 --> 00:01:09,000
I'll think of something.

14
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,000
Think of something?

15
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:12,159
You spend your days drinking and playing cards.

16
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,280
You even complained about delivering food.

17
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:16,040
What can you possibly come up with?

18
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,439
I... I'm just trash.

19
00:01:17,519 --> 00:01:18,120
Trash.

20
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:20,799
But my brother-in-law's clinic is booming.

21
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,200
I'm sure I can figure something out.

22
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,840
You mean

23
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:26,159
Lan Jianhua's clinic?

24
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:26,959
Exactly.

25
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,560
Shengxiu Hall.

26
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:29,959
Mr. Liu,

27
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:32,040
I can't run away from my responsibilities.

28
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:33,000
Give me ten more days.

29
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,280
I'm sure I can find a solution.

30
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,239
Alright,

31
00:01:36,719 --> 00:01:37,359
just ten days.

32
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,680
Okay, okay.

33
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,280
Okay.

34
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,519
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

35
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,319
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

36
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:45,799
Here, yours.

37
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,239
-Take it. -Thank you.

38
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:48,439
How much is this?

39
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,159
-19 yuan a cup. -I'll have one.

40
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:50,120
Just scan here.

41
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:53,159
[The chrysanthemum heart on the cross-section]

42
00:01:53,519 --> 00:01:54,760
[of the ginseng slice]

43
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,680
[is formed after 5 years of growth.]

44
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:59,359
[After three steaming and three sun-drying,]

45
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:02,439
[the ginseng's fierceness is boiled into...]

46
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,120
Dr. Lan,

47
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:07,879
we're filming a promotional video. Please cooperate.

48
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,039
Okay.

49
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,120
Later,

50
00:02:11,439 --> 00:02:12,639
I'll film you from here.

51
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,560
Cooperate, okay?

52
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,439
Okay.

53
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:15,400
Come on.

54
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:19,400
Let me see.

55
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,400
Are you okay?

56
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:31,039
That handsome guy inside just now

57
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,319
is the big blogger Lin Hao, right?

58
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:33,840
He's so close with Dr. Lan.

59
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,199
Are they together?

60
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,520
You...

61
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,319
What's your problem?

62
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:57,520
I'm here for the emergency.

63
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,879
Why do you suddenly have a neck pain?

64
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:13,879
I don't know.

65
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:15,400
It just hurts.

66
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:26,960
You're pressing too hard.

67
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,840
Be gentle when applying the medicine.

68
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,280
Such a fusspot.

69
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,759
When Xiaochuan sprained her ankle before,

70
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,039
she didn't even whimper.

71
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,080
I carried her to the hospital.

72
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:37,599
Right?

73
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:41,280
Xiaochuan is tough, I'm melodramatic?

74
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,960
When I fainted from anemia,

75
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:47,240
she carried me to the hospital.

76
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,159
Letting a girl take care of you,

77
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:50,400
are you that proud?

78
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:52,199
You're something.

79
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:54,159
I like strong-willed girls.

80
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,639
We complement each other,

81
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,840
and get along well.

82
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,960
Let Xiaochuan do it.

83
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:06,599
You're too unprofessional.

84
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:07,599
Wasting medicine.

85
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,199
Your technique is unprofessional.

86
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:12,479
I've treated you enough.

87
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,199
Are you two done?

88
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:32,639
Sit down.

89
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:39,160
Lin Hao,

90
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:40,480
I'm sorry.

91
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,240
You should go home and rest today.

92
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:48,279
As for you,

93
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,040
I think you're just looking for trouble today.

94
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,399
You have energy to burn, right?

95
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,040
Go

96
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,360
slice 10kg of ginseng.

97
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,920
Sweep up the shards outside.

98
00:04:55,079 --> 00:04:56,360
Then make three pots of ginseng tea.

99
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,319
Did you hear me?

100
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:08,360
She's making me work.

101
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,959
What are you doing here?

102
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,800
Helping out?

103
00:05:12,079 --> 00:05:12,800
Got a problem?

104
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,120
This is a good clip.

105
00:05:28,639 --> 00:05:29,720
I'll edit it later

106
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:30,920
and post it on the WeChat account.

107
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,000
Might even bring in some traffic.

108
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,120
You're cutting so slowly.

109
00:05:42,839 --> 00:05:44,000
Have you ever done this before?

110
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:50,480
Mine is thinner than yours.

111
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,680
Slow work makes fine products.

112
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,120
Who's talking?

113
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,319
You're interrupting my video.

114
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,399
Brother-in-law,

115
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:10,199
I've been feeling very chesty lately.

116
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,319
You, you,

117
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,560
take my pulse.

118
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,480
I'll go check.

119
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:21,759
You two keep cutting.

120
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:23,600
Why didn't you say earlier?

121
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:24,920
Let me check it for you.

122
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:25,879
Okay, okay.

123
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:27,399
What's going on?

124
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,160
Chuan,

125
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:30,240
go get your uncle a glass of water.

126
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,759
He has hands and feet.

127
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,839
Why doesn't he get it himself?

128
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,439
Your uncle

129
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,800
is sensible. Go.

130
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,040
Look, you spoiled him.

131
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,519
How can he be so rude?

132
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,439
Look at this.

133
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:16,319
This is the most popular ginseng tea recipe from Shengxiu Hall.

134
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,120
Find someone for me.

135
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,199
We'll follow their packaging

136
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,399
and specifications.

137
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,480
We'll make an identical batch.

138
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:26,680
But isn't this the exclusive recipe of the Lan family?

139
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,439
Where did you get this?

140
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:29,759
This, this, this...

141
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:30,839
You don't need to worry about that.

142
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,240
Just follow this to make it.

143
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:36,120
Isn't this counterfeiting? It's illegal.

144
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,279
What if Dr. Lan finds out?

145
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,160
He dares not.

146
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:41,120
Let me tell you.

147
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,399
He may be a big shot now,

148
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:44,199
but he has to

149
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,800
light cigarettes and pour drinks for me.

150
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,920
I won't drink unless he shows respect.

151
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,759
He owes me.

152
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:51,800
Even if he finds out,

153
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:53,839
he won't dare to do anything.

154
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:54,959
Trust me.

155
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,480
Let's

156
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,319
make a batch

157
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,319
and make a batch of it,

158
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,680
selling it at a low price in the market.

159
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:02,160
We'll make a fortune!

160
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,920
Alright, I'll give it a try.

161
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,079
Come on, Mr. Zhang,

162
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,199
have some tea.

163
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,079
Come on.

164
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:12,519
Hello,

165
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,680
Mr. Liu.

166
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:14,680
This is Xiaochuan.

167
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,160
I have a question for you.

168
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,639
Well,

169
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:21,199
if someone is counterfeiting my herbal tea

170
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,040
and trademark,

171
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,759
what should I do?

172
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,920
Sorry, Mr. Liu,

173
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,800
I'll call you back later.

174
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,519
What are you doing?

175
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:32,399
Hey, girl,

176
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,440
what are you doing

177
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:35,679
out here alone at this time?

178
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,639
Come here.

179
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:40,639
Let go of me!

180
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:41,679
Don't go anywhere!

181
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,440
Let go of me.

182
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:46,240
You are quite strong for a girl.

183
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:47,360
Let go of me.

184
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:47,840
Go.

185
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,840
-Go with me.  -Let go of me.

186
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,879
-Let go of me.  -Go.

187
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:06,399
Go away.

188
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,919
You pretty boy, who do you think you are?

189
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,360
I'll kill you, believe it or not?

190
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,120
Wait and see.

191
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,000
Wait and see.

192
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:45,480
Has he left?

193
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,240
Not yet.

194
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,519
When did he leave?

195
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:13,799
He left a long time ago.

196
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,159
You lied to me.

197
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:22,639
I just want to

198
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:24,960
stay with you a little longer.
